Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,祝您旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Please, list\N{\fs50}請給我名單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要找到擁有探索能力的能力者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去問問這個頭目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:32.30,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,71)\fad(500,500)}菲律賓  市區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  他會擁有什麼樣的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}If you move, you fire\N{\fs50}你要是動了  你就著火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Your leader?\N{\fs50}你是頭目？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Who are you?\N{\fs50}你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Unusual ability player\N{\fs50}能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Why I can't read his mind!?\N{\fs50}為什麼我讀不了他的心？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Why I can't read...\N{\fs50}為什麼我讀不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}He stole my ability!?\N{\fs50}我的能力被他偷去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}That's right\N{\fs50}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這能力真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Question\N{\fs50}提問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}What do you look unusual ability player?\N{\fs50}你是怎麼找能力者的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Don't think, don't think, don't think...\N{\fs50}別思考  別思考  別思考…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,安傑洛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這傢伙找到能力者的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Thank you\N{\fs50}謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Damn you...\N{\fs50}你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Goddamnit\N{\fs50}該死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Door, open up!\N{\fs50}把門打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}What?\h\N{\fs50}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Are you Angelo?\h\N{\fs50}你就是安傑洛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Who are you?\h\N{\fs50}你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}What do you want from me?\N{\fs50}你想要我幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Ability is sickness\N{\fs50}能力是種病症
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}You not used ability\N{\fs50}你不再使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}Oh gosh\N{\fs50}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看地圖就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,堪稱完美的能力者探知能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:42.89,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,77)\fad(500,500)}南非共和國  北部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs32}Earlier this morning,\N{\fs44}今晨稍早些時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs32}the UN announced that the democratic revolutionary army,\N{\fs44}聯合國宣佈廣泛分佈在亞洲多個地區的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs32}an organization based in various parts of Asia,\N{\fs44}民主革命軍組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs32}had been subjugated.\N{\fs44}已經宣佈投降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs32}The UN Chairman Brian Jackson reported that "a young...\N{\fs44}據聯合國發言人布萊恩•傑克遜披露  一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}…少年毫髮無損地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}將其組織幹部全員逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}就今後的形勢問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}他表示將警惕殘餘勢力的反撲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}並對未來的和平進程表示樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這麼方便的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還有其他幾個地方聚集著能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.26,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,73)\fad(500,500)}埃及  市區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635,660)}要警惕獨眼的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,獨眼的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,居然給我取這麼羞恥的外號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒想到我竟然會被這麼稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那個映像是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不知何時起  我已經能知道自己所奪取的能力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我又奪取了一個國家所有能力者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我奪取了翻譯語言的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還得手了就算不睡覺也能正常活動的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是別太勉強自己了  有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不  下一個國家我也得儘快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,時間不等人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但一定要趕在你失去能力之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,使病情加重的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:53.85,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,77)}阿富汗  山區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能力者又聚集在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,居然讓孩子做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊只有一個閃光點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  什麼映像都沒出現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡究竟是什麼設施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,帶原者？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然被感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是還沒發作出能力  所以是帶原者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我無法奪取還沒有發作的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特殊能力正是一種病症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以得在下次粒子散播到地球上之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,讓全世界的人接種疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是病症的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以讓其惡化以激發出能力  不就能奪取了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好  行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,為了保證我離開以後這個國家裡不再出現能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,從今往後帶原者的能力也必須奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:24.20,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,73)\fad(500,500)}印度  東部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,打到沒子彈為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:54.19,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,77)\fad(500,500)}秘魯共和國  郊外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是有的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,治癒能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}能治好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  就算妳用來行善
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不得不奪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要是現在用這隻手觸碰右眼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能重新獲得時間跳躍的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定就能救下熊耳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是為了這個才奪取別人的能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再做出違背世事常理的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命是讓這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不再有能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.80,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(1065,77)\fad(500,500)}古巴共和國  市區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
